<br>
Many of you probably do not know of the character Fermaga, but a few of you do.  I have tried, to the best of my abilities, to show compasion and support to all who ask.  This includes my current guild and former guild.  What i dont understand, and please, i know its rants and flames, but truthful honest answers would help, is why would someone no longer want to talk to you because of someone or thing that another has done?  I wont go into details because i think they are just not worth causing more grief.  It seems i have lost a few friends by what is being quoted as &quot;Guilt by Association&quot;. One individual in particular i had shared such information that i thought we could be great friends in RL.  It was by her pain that I was prompted to post this since it was said that what someone else is doing whom I am friends with has decided to cut off all ties.<br>
<br>
<br>
This is a game I thought.  People take it to such a degree that what happens in game is RL.  Perhaps this is a sign, with me posting such a message, that I am taking this too seriously.  Just ranting a little cause quite frankly, Im at a loss.<br>
<br>
